{"tid":1772804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警拘人叠人傷者 阻消防救援五小時","createTime":"2019-12-07T03:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T05:34:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78f6b3efe3d861f0b4625cf5b15c524d054ddc6b","tid":1772804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/MOK5WVOSMRPFXVAJ4OSE37YGGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2FMOK5WVOSMRPFXVAJ4OSE37YGGQ%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=22842fcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2FMOK5WVOSMRPFXVAJ4OSE37YGGQ%2F&h=dbce1b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/MOK5WVOSMRPFXVAJ4OSE37YGGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n警拘人叠人傷者 阻消防救援五小時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575648665_d424.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575648665_d424.gif&h=cad55a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上月18日因警方圍捕而造成「人叠人」慘劇。Kaiser圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上月18日晚油麻地大批市民遭警方圍捕，釀成「人叠人」的情況。《蘋果》日前披露的一份疑似消防處內部紀錄，揭示現場傷者因等待警方分流而延誤送院；消防處昨再度回應事件，證實消防人員在分流和治理傷者時「需不時與警方協調」，確認事件中最後一名需送院傷者於凌晨4時半才送往聯合醫院，距離消防人員發現「人叠人」，相隔五個小時之久。<br />\n<br />\n共33人送院治理<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：飛行服務隊 懲教 受累評分跌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消防處昨進一步回應《蘋果》就人叠人事件的查詢，指消防於晚上11時32分發現油麻地港鐵站A1出口與寶寧大廈之間的通道出現「人叠人」，通訊中心隨即增派另外九輛消防車及41輛救護車到現場處理。<br />\n<br />\n處方指消防人員用約十分鐘將30多名被困者拯救到安全地方，按消防處的講法，救護人員在處理傷者時，警方仍在現場進行拘捕行動，令救援人員在評估、分流及治理傷者時「需不時與警方協調」；其中當值助理消防區長於凌晨1時07分通報消防通訊中心，指現場大約有150名示威者被警方拘捕，但無法確定傷者人數，消防人員亦要「在警方的協助下」進行傷者分流工作；不過處方稱沒有收到消防人員被警員阻撓救援的報告。<br />\n<br />\n消防處指事故中共將17名嚴重、14名普通及兩名輕傷的傷者，共33人送往醫院治理，其餘所有在場人士則「由警方處理」；而現場最後一名需要送院傷者於凌晨4時半才被送往聯合醫院，距離消防人員發現「人叠人」的時間，相隔達五個小時之久。而警方回應指當日傷者的分流安排由救護人員負責。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛"},{"pid":"863e966deaddcad72e60f02ddbef2c98ce7d9967","tid":1772804,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/3631088/org/b7ee80d03d91661dce9ca530bb2b3c87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3631088%2Forg%2Fb7ee80d03d91661dce9ca530bb2b3c87.jpg&h=6c7c5e0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2cf5a69872b99492e6178295381ebd8f409cfd0","tid":1772804,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"863e966deaddcad72e60f02ddbef2c98ce7d9967","tid":1772804,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/3631088/org/b7ee80d03d91661dce9ca530bb2b3c87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3631088%2Forg%2Fb7ee80d03d91661dce9ca530bb2b3c87.jpg&h=6c7c5e0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/403296/11-18-%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%8A%E4%BA%BA-cctv%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E8%AD%89%E8%AD%A6%E9%A9%85%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%93%A1-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%86%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%8A%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A5%2F403296%2F11-18-%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2596%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA-cctv%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A0%2586%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E5%258A%2591&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=40000d69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/403296/11-18-%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%8A%E4%BA%BA-cctv%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E8%AD%89%E8%AD%A6%E9%A9%85